title: Layla El
summary: Layla El (born 25 June 1977) is an English real estate agent and former dancer, model, and retired professional wrestler. She is best known for her time with WWE, where she performed under the mononymous ring name Layla. She danced for Carnival Cruise Lines, the Miami Heat franchise of the National Basketball Association, and Kanye West during his performance at the MTV Video Music Awards before becoming a contestant on the 2006 edition of WWE's Diva Search, which she won to earn a contract with the company.
